odase.swrl

Class SwrlBuiltinResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • odase.swrl.SwrlBuiltinResult
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    SwrlBuiltinResult.Failure, SwrlBuiltinResult.Success, SwrlBuiltinResult.UnboundVar, SwrlBuiltinResult.Unsupported

    public abstract class SwrlBuiltinResult
extends Object
    SwrlBuiltinResult is a sum type which describes the result of a builtin call. 4 distinct cases are covered:
    • SwrlBuiltinResult.Success: the builtin call admits at least one solution. Each solution is a possible substitution of the variable parameters.
    • SwrlBuiltinResult.Failure: the builtin call admits no solution. An explanation message may be specified.
    • SwrlBuiltinResult.Unsupported: the required builtin is not supported by the builtin structure
    • SwrlBuiltinResult.UnboundVar: the parameters of the builtin are not instanciated enough to allow a computation
    Author:
    llg
